{"tid":1829927,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Cyberpunk 2077 電馭叛客 延期推出！CD Projekt RED發文證實","createTime":"2020-01-19T08:13:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-14T01:33:44.000Z","uid":85180,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"122a00555140e26ec21b80840cb64939d4e3a768","tid":1829927,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T08:13:21.000Z","msg":"Cyberpunk 2077 電馭叛客 延期推出！CD Projekt RED發文證實<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/cis/5e213be4b66f770df1c20971.jpeg/FMlXbEazQOyKPO2NTxqvB6BeupI-udxxTSxMkk0sTJI?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fcis%2F5e213be4b66f770df1c20971.jpeg%2FFMlXbEazQOyKPO2NTxqvB6BeupI-udxxTSxMkk0sTJI%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=f6361df8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【Cyberpunk 2077 延期】繼Square Enix《Final Fantasy XII Remake》、《復仇者聯盟》宣布延期推出後，另一大廠CD Projekt Red的AAA級重頭科幻RPG大作《Cyberpunk 2077》（電馭叛客）原定於2020年4月16日推出的希望已成泡影，製作團隊於香港時間1月17日凌晨在社交媒體上發文，宣布PS4、Xbox One及PC版遊戲延期消息！<br />\n<br />\n早前日本TGS 2019東京電玩展上，製作《The Witcher 3：Wild Hunt》的CD Projekt RED團隊曾非常有信心，於TGS上設有大型展區，同時讓傳媒於業務日中試玩DEMO，以下重溫我們於TGS中的詳細試玩報告。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/cis/5e20abf7b66f770df1c20839.jpg/kB117--xhjN3IvugmJ2n1KIXbxhkugdqnXV2sJ11drA?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fcis%2F5e20abf7b66f770df1c20839.jpg%2FkB117--xhjN3IvugmJ2n1KIXbxhkugdqnXV2sJ11drA%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=4f77f0a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有「K先生」奇洛李維斯（Kenau Reeves）挾著《John Wick 3》電影之勢，《Cyberpunk 2077》更叫玩家引頸以待，可惜突然宣布延期！【CD Projekt RED】<br />\n<br />\nCD Projekt Red創辦人Marcin Iwinski及CDPR製作室總監Adam Badowski於1月17日凌晨，透過官方Facebook及Twitter上發表公告，兩者同時以「We have important news regarding Cyberpunk 2077&rsquo;s release date we&rsquo;d like to share with you today.」（今天我們希望與你分享有關Cyberpunk 2077推出日期的重要消息）為題，點按圖片才能觀看這重要內容。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/cis/5e20aafafd5cc31c9c2bc2d1.jpg/TCHO057ivxna36uwdjcjoX5BBqxE9d4r4sr41uLK-NY?v=w640\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fcis%2F5e20aafafd5cc31c9c2bc2d1.jpg%2FTCHO057ivxna36uwdjcjoX5BBqxE9d4r4sr41uLK-NY%3Fv%3Dw640&h=c6dd96c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/cis/5e20acfd23ab170deb424d87.jpg/NDUSjgmrbLbLSywzzbHSjTONP5hUluqT5gVAIuYFQCI?v=w640\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fcis%2F5e20acfd23ab170deb424d87.jpg%2FNDUSjgmrbLbLSywzzbHSjTONP5hUluqT5gVAIuYFQCI%3Fv%3Dw640&h=bdadd4d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EOa2ITXW4AAbcag?format=png&amp;name=small\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEOa2ITXW4AAbcag%3Fformat%3Dpng%26name%3Dsmall&h=8c2c6353&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nCD Projekt RED對《Cyberpunk 2077》的延期公布節錄如下：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>Cyberpunk 2077 won't make the April release window and we're moving the launch date to September 17, 2020<br />\n「Cyber​​punk 2077不會在4月推出，我們會將（遊戲的）推出日期推遲至2020年9月17日。」</strong></span><br />\n<br />\nWe are currently at a stage where the game is complete and playable, but there's still work to be done. Night City is massive - full of stories, content, and places to visit, but due to the sheer scale and complexity of it all, we need more time to finish playtesting, fixing and polishing.<br />\n「目前（遊戲）處於完整且可玩的階段，但我們仍有工作要做。（遊戲舞台）Night City是一個非常龐大，充滿故事、內容及地方探索，但由於其規模之大和複雜 ，需要更多時間來完成測試，修復和改善遊戲。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/cis/5e20a38c13d12b1ca2b94016.jpg/f6mr6uKTackLSIGFCtJCfnAcGuPJdRtmf92A73_dgO8?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fcis%2F5e20a38c13d12b1ca2b94016.jpg%2Ff6mr6uKTackLSIGFCtJCfnAcGuPJdRtmf92A73_dgO8%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=8edc9c56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nCyber​​punk 2077 的Night City極為龐大，成為遊戲延期理由 【CD Projekt RED】<br />\n<br />\n這是《Cyberpunk 2077》的第三度宣布延期，在此之前原定推出日為本年4月16日，推遲近半年才有得玩，唯有看看官方公布的遊戲實機影片止渴吧。"},{"pid":"b1380faa3c63660c4df5148ac83f962c33493a81","tid":1829927,"uid":191150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T08:37:30.000Z","msg":"good"},{"pid":"cdaf3c942dd942e1d95118aa631000d849d91b48","tid":1829927,"uid":39383,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T08:39:46.000Z","msg":"之前好似話過地圖無witcher 3 咁大, 但可探索地方就多左, 好撚期待"},{"pid":"ee4d865a8428c5ebb58273e29ef1c56b0be8cf96","tid":1829927,"uid":82889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T08:40:27.000Z","msg":"一篇新聞貼三次"},{"pid":"691b3f7e319a43afd4d0ed000537eff1184a2ad4","tid":1829927,"uid":166766,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"cdaf3c942dd942e1d95118aa631000d849d91b48","tid":1829927,"uid":39383,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T08:39:46.000Z","msg":"之前好似話過地圖無witcher 3 咁大, 但可探索地方就多左, 好撚期待"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T09:10:32.000Z","msg":"應該係垂直探索空間更大<br />\n未來世界大廈高咁多"},{"pid":"5596cf5bf891f3006a674ef69bfea43720b392f7","tid":1829927,"uid":22700,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T09:45:11.000Z","msg":"Ciri去過2077<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d5b8ca3b3e8333dc86f34fb45a76654684adb5e","tid":1829927,"uid":133387,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5596cf5bf891f3006a674ef69bfea43720b392f7","tid":1829927,"uid":22700,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T09:45:11.000Z","msg":"Ciri去過2077<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T20:41:49.000Z","msg":"Witcher 3 你打主線剛搵返 Ciri 時佢有講過...<br />\n佢識時間魔法，話自己去過一個異世界有好多科幻野<br />\n果時好多人估到係暗示去左 2077個世界 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a5